org.apache.poi.xwpf.usermodel

Enum UnderlinePatterns

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<UnderlinePatterns>
      • org.apache.poi.xwpf.usermodel.UnderlinePatterns
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<UnderlinePatterns> 

    public enum UnderlinePatterns
extends java.lang.Enum<UnderlinePatterns>
    Specifies the types of patterns which may be used to create the underline applied beneath the text in a run.(指定可用于创建应用于线条中文本下方的下线的模式类型。)
    Author:
    Gisella Bronzetti

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      DASH
      Specifies an underline consisting of a dashed line beneath all characters in this run.(指定此运行中所有字符下方由虚线组成的下线。)
      DASH_DOT_DOT_HEAVY
      Specifies an underline consisting of a series of thick dash, dot, dot characters beneath all characters in this run.(指定由此运行中所有字符下方的一系列粗破折号、圆点、圆点字符组成的下线。)

      DOTTED_HEAVY
      Specifies an underline consisting of a series of thick dot characters beneath all characters in this run.(指定由一系列粗点字符组成的下划线，位于此行程中的所有字符之下。)
      DOUBLE
      Specifies an underline consisting of two lines beneath all characters in this run(指定此运行中所有字符下方由两行组成的下线)
      NONE
      Specifies no underline beneath this run.(指定此运行下没有下划线。)
      SINGLE
      Specifies an underline consisting of a single line beneath all characters in this run.(指定此运行中所有字符下方由一行组成的下线。)
      THICK
      Specifies an underline consisting of a single thick line beneath all characters in this run.(指定此运行中所有字符下方由一条粗线组成的下线。)
      WAVE
      Specifies an underline consisting of a single wavy line beneath all characters in this run.(指定此运行中所有字符下方由单个波浪线组成的下线。)
      WAVY_DOUBLE

      WORDS
      Specifies an underline consisting of a single line beneath all non-space characters in the run.(指定在运行中所有非空白字符下方由一行组成的下划线。)

      • WORDS

        public static final UnderlinePatterns WORDS
        Specifies an underline consisting of a single line beneath all non-space characters in the run. There shall be no underline beneath any space character (breaking or non-breaking).(指定在运行中所有非空白字符下方由一行组成的下划线。任何空白字符下方均不得有任何划线（断开或非断开）。)
